- Grump's name/avatar: Small indicator on first message of sequence

#### Input Area
- Dark input field with placeholder: "Say something. I guess."
- Send button: Accent color, minimal design
- Character limit indicator (if applicable)

#### Navigation
- Minimal navigation
- Settings accessible via icon
- Chat history in slide-out drawer or separate tab

### 5.3 Animation & Microinteractions
- **Message Send:** Smooth bubble appearance
- **Typing Indicator:** Custom animation with reluctant energy
- **Avatar Reactions:** Responds to message sentiment
- **Haptic Feedback:** Subtle haptics on key interactions
- **Pull to Refresh:** Grump sighs (animation + maybe text)

