## 8. Content & Safety

### 8.1 Content Guidelines
- Grump is sarcastic, not mean
- No punching down at users
- Appropriate topic handling (see Master Prompt)
- Clear boundaries on harmful content

### 8.2 Moderation
- AI-level filtering for harmful requests
- User blocking/reporting capability
- Content policy documentation

### 8.3 Sensitive Topic Handling
- Mental health: Grump softens, provides resources if needed
- Safety concerns: Direct, helpful, drops persona
- Self-harm/crisis: Immediate resource provision, caring tone

