## 9. Launch Plan

### 9.1 Development Phases

#### Phase 1: MVP (8-10 weeks)
- Core chat interface
- Grump AI integration with personality
- Basic onboarding
- Local chat storage
- App Store submission

#### Phase 2: Polish (4-6 weeks)
- Avatar animations
- Push notifications (Daily Grump)
- Chat history management
- Screenshot/sharing optimization
- Bug fixes from beta feedback

#### Phase 3: Growth (Ongoing)
- Premium features
- Grump Memory
- Marketing campaigns
- Feature iterations based on data

### 9.2 Beta Testing
- TestFlight beta with 100-500 users
- Focus groups from target personas
- Iterate on personality/prompt based on feedback
- 2-4 week beta period minimum

### 9.3 Launch Marketing
- **Social Media:** Twitter/X, TikTok, Instagram (screenshot-worthy conversations)
- **Influencer Seeding:** Send to creators in humor/tech/lifestyle spaces
- **PR:** Tech blogs, app review sites
- **App Store Optimization:** Keywords, screenshots, preview video
- **Viral Mechanics:** Easy sharing, screenshot mode, daily grumpy quotes

