## 10. Risks & Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|------------|
| AI responses break character | High | Medium | Robust system prompt, testing, fallback responses |
| API costs exceed budget | High | Medium | Rate limiting, caching, usage tiers |
| App Store rejection | High | Low | Review guidelines compliance, content moderation |
| Low retention | High | Medium | Notification strategy, engagement features, content variety |
| Copycat apps | Medium | High | Brand building, community, feature velocity |
| Negative reception | Medium | Low | Beta testing, iteration, clear positioning |

